id: 2719
name: "6069 Dictatorship"
power: 1.0
text: |
  ais523 CAN cause this rule to amend itself with support from
  Janet. Janet CAN cause this rule to amend itself with support from
  ais523.

  If at any point (including points in the middle of a public
  message) a player other than ais523 or Janet would have more than
  24 Spendies, all but 24 of that player's Spendies are
  automatically and immediately revoked from that player.

  ais523 CAN grant emself any number of Spendies by announcement.
  Janet CAN grant emself any number of Spendies by announcement.
